episodes.title: Doug Kramer Grew Up with Scientology and Escaped at 33
episodes.description: Doug Scott Kramer is a Los Angeles-based actor who was raised in Scientology and escaped at the age of 33. He recently started making a series of videos documenting what this whole insane experience was like.  Check out his channel at https://www.youtube.com/user/Rainez024   *************************************************************** And don’t forget to support the podcast by subscribing for free, reviewing, and sharing.
